data.text:
About

Conveniently located next to the Historic Pottery Mall. Close to restaurants and shopping. Near Cannon Valley Bike Trail. Indoor Pool and Whirlpool, Free High Speed Wireless Internet, Free Continental Breakfast. Whirlpool suites available for those romantic outings. Close to Fishing and Golfing. Call for prompt, friendly service. We offer 36 single and double rooms and 3 unique suites (Jacuzzi, kitchenette,3-bedroom). Conveniently located next to the Historic Pottery Place Outlet Mall, restaurants and lounges. Near Treasure Island Casino, Cannon Valley biking and walking trail, golf, skiing (Welch Village and Mount Frontenac)and water sports on the Mississippi River. We also feature 60% non-smoking rooms, free local calls, remote control color TV, VCR movies, fax and copier service, handicap facilities, quiet location and ample parking. 50 miles from Minneapolis/St. Paul and the Mall of America.
